t><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://plausible.io/js/script.js\" as=\"script\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Cher Ami</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Share memories with your family\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.3ef307f3.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/a6dad97d9634a72d.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"poppins_52ca281-module__qdtoBq__className\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"bg-[#FCFBF8] pt-5\"><div class=\"flex flex-row justify-between items-center w-full max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-5\"><a href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Cher Ami logo\" width=\"143\" height=\"32\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-[143px] h-8 flex-none\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ftitle.3ba23643.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ftitle.3ba23643.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ftitle.3ba23643.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></a><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-4\"><a class=\"text-[#B05637] px-4 py-3 rounded-xl\" href=\"/#steps-section\">How It Works</a><a class=\"text-[#B05637] px-4 py-3 rounded-xl\" href=\"/help\">Help</a><a class=\"bg-[#C15F3C] text-[#FFFFFF] px-4 py-3 rounded-xl\" href=\"#download-section\">Get Cher Ami</a></div></div></header><div class=\"bg-[#FCFBF8] py-36\"><main class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-y-36 pb-5\"><section class=\"flex flex-row items-center\"><div class=\"flex-1 hidden xl:block\"><img alt=\"A hedgehog holding balloons.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"287\" height=\"399\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fhedgehog.ddc3eee6.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fhedgehog.ddc3eee6.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fhedgehog.ddc3eee6.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12\">Share your cherished memories of family and friends.</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center max-w-xl mx-auto mb-16\">Every month, your circle&#x27;s best photos are transformed into a beautiful magazine and delivered to loved ones&#x27; doorsteps.</p></div><div class=\"flex-1 hidden xl:block\"><img alt=\"A mouse throwing a paper airplane.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"291\" height=\"485\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fmouse.200061ed.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fmouse.200061ed.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fmouse.200061ed.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></section><section><div class=\"mb-10\"><h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto pb-5\">Two ways to connect.</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center max-w-xl mx-auto\">Sharing moments of your life with family and friends has never been easier.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 mb-20\"><img alt=\"An smartphone running the Cher Ami mobile app\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"593\" height=\"803\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"block w-auto h-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fapp-showcase.3def1b48.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fapp-showcase.3def1b48.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fapp-showcase.3def1b48.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75\"/><img alt=\"The Cher Ami magazine\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"775\" height=\"803\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"block w-auto h-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fmagazine-showcase.02e4a40a.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fmagazine-showcase.02e4a40a.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fmagazine-showcase.02e4a40a.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></section><section class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"mb-10\"><h2 id=\"steps-section\" class=\"text-[2.5rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto pb-5\">As easy as...</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center max-w-xl mx-auto\">You focus on making memories while we take care of everything else, from design to delivery.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"relative w-[350px] flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"absolute -top-6 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-16 h-16 bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"The number one\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"18\" height=\"22\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-one.7bb52392.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-one.7bb52392.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-one.7bb52392.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-4xl p-7 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col h-[255px] justify-center\"><img alt=\"Three mice playing with a kite\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"235\" height=\"255\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-one-illustration.4e4013c4.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-one-illustration.4e4013c4.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-one-illustration.4e4013c4.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><h2 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#C15F3C] font-semibold text-center mt-6 mb-2\">Share Photos</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center\">Upload memories through our app all month long.</p></div></div><div class=\"relative w-[350px] flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"absolute -top-6 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-16 h-16 bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"The number two\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"26.61\" height=\"30.86\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-two.74bf54a6.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-two.74bf54a6.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-two.74bf54a6.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-4xl p-7 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col h-[255px] justify-center\"><img alt=\"A squirrel delivering a letter\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"311\" height=\"255\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-two-illustration.f240724c.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-two-illustration.f240724c.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-two-illustration.f240724c.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><h2 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#C15F3C] font-semibold text-center mt-6 mb-2\">Receive Magazine</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center\">Upload memories through our app all month long.</p></div></div><div class=\"relative w-[350px] flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"absolute -top-6 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-16 h-16 bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\"><img alt=\"The number three\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"22\" height=\"26\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-three.ee14aa4f.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-three.ee14aa4f.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-three.ee14aa4f.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-4xl p-7 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col h-[255px] justify-center\"><img alt=\"A family of bears reading a magazine\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"245\" height=\"255\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-three-illustration.eed0c87a.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-three-illustration.eed0c87a.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fstep-three-illustration.eed0c87a.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div><h2 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#C15F3C] font-semibold text-center mt-6 mb-2\">Enjoy Together</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center\">Upload memories through our app all month long.</p></div></div></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10\">Pricing</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-t-[20] border-t-2 border-l-2 border-r-2 border-[#F4F1EA] items-center bg-[#F4F1EA] py-2 w-full\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold\">Digital Edition</h3></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center pl-6 pr-6 pb-6 rounded-b-[20] border-b-2 border-l-2 border-r-2 border-[#F4F1EA]\"><h3 class=\"text-[3rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold my-4\">FREE</h3><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1\"><img alt=\"A check mark\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/_next/static/media/check.cf8bc457.svg\"/><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal\">Share and view posts on the Cher Ami app.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1\"><img alt=\"A check mark\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/_next/static/media/check.cf8bc457.svg\"/><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal\">Add unlimited members to your circle.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1\"><img alt=\"The letter X\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/_next/static/media/x.6839fb8c.svg\"/><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal\">No printed magazine.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1]\"><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-transparent font-normal\">Free shipping</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-t-[20] border-t-2 border-l-2 border-r-2 border-[#C15F3C] items-center bg-[#C15F3C] py-2 w-full\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#FCFBF8] font-semibold\">Monthly Edition</h3></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center pl-6 pr-6 pb-6 rounded-b-[20] border-b-2 border-l-2 border-r-2 border-[#C15F3C]\"><h3 class=\"text-[3rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold my-4\">$12.99</h3><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1\"><img alt=\"A check mark\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/_next/static/media/check.cf8bc457.svg\"/><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal\">Share and view posts on the Cher Ami app.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1\"><img alt=\"A check mark\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/_next/static/media/check.cf8bc457.svg\"/><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal\">Add unlimited members to your circle.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1\"><img alt=\"A check mark\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/_next/static/media/check.cf8bc457.svg\"/><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal\">Receive a printed magazine each month.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-x-1\"><img alt=\"A check mark\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/_next/static/media/check.cf8bc457.svg\"/><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal\">Free shipping.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10\">Our values</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-4xl p-7 flex flex-col items-center w-[350px]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col h-[255px] justify-center\"><img alt=\"A mouse smoking a pipe\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"156\" height=\"183\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-quality.2ee5612b.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-quality.2ee5612b.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-quality.2ee5612b.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></div><h2 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#C15F3C] font-semibold text-center mt-6 mb-2\">High Quality</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center\">Upload memories through our app all month long.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-4xl p-7 flex flex-col items-center w-[350px]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col h-[255px] justify-center\"><img alt=\"A mouse picking up acorns\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"156\" height=\"183\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-privacy.f36f681b.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-privacy.f36f681b.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-privacy.f36f681b.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></div><h2 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#C15F3C] font-semibold text-center mt-6 mb-2\">Private</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center\">Upload memories through our app all month long.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-4xl p-7 flex flex-col items-center w-[350px]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col h-[255px] justify-center\"><img alt=\"A paper airplane\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"156\" height=\"183\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-shipping.53967923.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-shipping.53967923.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fvalue-shipping.53967923.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></div><h2 class=\"text-[1.75rem] text-[#C15F3C] font-semibold text-center mt-6 mb-2\">Free Shipping</h2><p class=\"text-[1rem] text-[#242832] font-normal text-center\">Upload memories through our app all month long.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] text-[#242832] font-semibold text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10\">What people are saying</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-[#F4F1EA] rounded-3xl p-5 w-[300px] flex flex-col\"><p class=\"text-[16px] text-[#242832] font-normal\">Such a delightful experience! The process was seamless, and the final gazette looked even better than we had hoped.</p><div class=\"flex flex-row items-center gap-x-2 mt-5\"><img alt=\"Kimi\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-full\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2F